\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A 
\series bold
mismatch between assets & liabilities
\series default
 can occur, when domestic corporations borrow USD, while their profits are
 in the domestic currency.
 It creates vulnerability when the domestic currency depreciates and the
 companies might default.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Israel was in a transition state at that time with a 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

diagonal
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

